Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.23,0:00:06.13,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,FAMOUS DETECTIVE HOLMES
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.08,0:01:41.19,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Did You See the Big Shining Thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.69,0:02:08.28,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.60,0:02:09.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:21.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,One million?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.58,0:02:23.81,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,One million pounds worth\Nof English gold bullion!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:26.25,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This should never have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.35,0:02:27.34,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.42,0:02:29.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what,\NI want you to arrest the thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:32.29,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Inspector Lestrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.39,0:02:34.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!\NLeave this matter to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:41.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.54,0:02:46.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the work of a professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:03:00.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't even touch the cash,\Nonly the heavy gold bullion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:05.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I checked before I left last\Nnight, the gold bullion was here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.03,0:03:09.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,How could they move one million pounds\Nworth of gold bullion, so quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.90,0:03:11.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector! Inspector, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:12.20,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:15.43,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,My job will be in jeopardy\Nif you don't arrest the thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:17.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.77,0:03:19.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:21.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Just relax and wait for the solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:23.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.81,0:03:26.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, let's begin\Na thorough investigation!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:27.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:29.62,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I really appreciate this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:42.29,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't find anything unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:43.42,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even one piece of broken glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:45.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No evidence that it was\Ncarried out through the windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.63,0:03:47.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector, can you find the thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.34,0:03:49.89,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave everything to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:03:59.08,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you eat while it's still hot,\Notherwise it won't be tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:03:59.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:03.38,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I have a bad habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.02,0:04:07.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Holmes, it seems like something\Nhas been bothering you recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:09.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been a week...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.96,0:04:13.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,but the London Police's investigation\Nhasn't been progressing well at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:14.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:16.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that the bank's\Nsafe was recently broken into.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:20.30,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,In the newspaper, Inspector Lestrade\Ndeclared that the case was simple...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:23.13,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,but he still hasn't found any clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.54,0:04:26.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing they're doing\Nis making me frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.88,0:04:30.54,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless we get involved, this\Ncase will never be solved, Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:34.18,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're really having a hard time,\Nthe Inspector will come to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:36.14,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so easy going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:38.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's one million pounds\Nworth of gold bullion!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:40.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.96,0:04:46.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Perison is still missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:48.25,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Perison?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.40,0:04:50.26,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a popular sculptor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:53.56,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He has won a lot of awards because\Nof his unique creative style.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.30,0:04:57.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about\Nthe stolen gold bullion!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:05:00.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The day Mr. Perison disappeared was the\Nday after the gold bullion was stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:02.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's related to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:04.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,A thief steals a large amount\Nof gold bullion...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:06.88,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,and a skilled sculptor goes missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:13.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! The thief is planning\Nto coin fake money!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.92,0:05:17.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard of anyone making\Nfake money from real gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:20.73,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how are they connected?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.83,0:05:22.09,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This has become an interesting case!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:23.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:26.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!\NThat's the spirit, Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.37,0:05:28.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but what about dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:30.07,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll eat that later!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:32.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's not nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.62,0:05:47.21,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,So your husband, Mr. Perison...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:49.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,after leaving with his\Npainting materials...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:50.59,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,has failed to return for three days?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:54.12,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he said he was supposed to paint\Na portrait of the American millionaire...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:55.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Sallinger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:05:59.73,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:05.60,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the sketches\Nhe was drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.74,0:06:11.44,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like he was\Ntrying to sculpt a bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:18.08,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he didn't like those sketches,\Nso he left with our son to redo them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:20.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Your son went with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.82,0:06:25.32,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he said he'd be back shortly\Nand left with our son, Copit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:29.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But, they haven't returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.17,0:06:33.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,If his son is with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:34.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,this might be trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.84,0:06:38.31,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But if this is the only clue...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.74,0:06:42.80,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Watson, did you notice that the person\Nin the sketchbook looks familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:45.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Looks familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:47.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:59.55,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Holmes, I was actually thinking\Nabout visiting you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:12.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you show me the fastest way to the\Nunderground safe from the back door?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:15.08,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh? Yes, I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.48,0:07:17.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see a lot of scratches on the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.65,0:07:20.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Inspector Lestrade\Nordered us to leave them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.45,0:07:21.38,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this hook for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.45,0:07:24.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Lestrade experimented with\Nways to carry out the gold bullion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:35.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It took the same amount of time from\Nthe back door as it did from the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:38.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanted to carry one million\Npounds worth of gold bullion...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.23,0:07:39.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,you couldn't do it in one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.57,0:07:43.33,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the way to the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.91,0:07:48.34,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The lock on this\Ndoor was broken, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:50.88,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's already been fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:53.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It was like this at the front entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:58.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this!\NOnly the gold bullion is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:05.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Inspector Lestrade\Ninvestigate this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:11.13,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Inspector Lestrade's investigation\Nwas for the most part outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.33,0:08:12.89,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.10,0:08:15.30,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There are marks indicating\Nthat somebody moved the shelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:16.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Then there is an entrance\Nbehind this shelf?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.11,0:08:17.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:20.60,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This room is surrounded\Nby a thick brick wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:22.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,May I move this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.01,0:08:24.00,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you may.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:26.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stand there watching us.\NGive us a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:28.07,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:32.88,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:41.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Holmes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:47.73,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The wall is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:54.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the gold bullion?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:56.87,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They dug this entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:09:00.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,If they used this entrance, they\Nshouldn't have had to break the lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:02.91,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They might have done\Nthis to trick the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.65,0:09:08.45,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but can you get\Nthe gold bullion back?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.26,0:09:11.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, my job will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:13.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think they could've carried\Nthe gold through this shabby tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:15.09,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it's about to collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.33,0:09:17.30,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:18.26,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:19.33,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There's light.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:20.37,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.80,0:09:23.77,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind place is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:25.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it connects to the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:27.84,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.14,0:09:30.11,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:32.41,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a caterpillar tread.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:36.31,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It continues all the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:37.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's follow this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:45.42,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This case is getting smelly,\Nisn't it Holmes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.46,0:09:48.59,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We're getting close to the exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.96,0:09:50.73,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear the sound of water\Ngoing into the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.47,0:09:53.20,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we going to travel\Nalong with sewage?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:58.10,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it hardly matters,\NI'm already dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:06.14,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:09.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.97,0:10:30.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well. Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.54,0:10:38.38,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,If they carried it off by boat from\Nhere, there's no way to trace them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:42.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But what if it could run on the ground,\Nand then become a ship on the water?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:44.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:46.15,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about an amphibious vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.05,0:10:48.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,An amphibious vehicle?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:03.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems we're going to have\Na lot of heavy work on this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:06.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.66,0:11:30.29,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Watson, I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:31.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.47,0:11:32.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.49,0:11:52.78,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.09,0:11:55.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,All that remains are the tread marks\Nof a caterpillar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.72,0:11:58.56,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the thief probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:37.20,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. This is a complicated caper.\NIt must be the work of Moriarty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:40.20,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,If we follow along the river,\Nwe can trace him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.37,0:12:41.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.37,0:12:43.80,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to walk along\Nthe river under water?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:07.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find something, Holmes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:09.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They must have gotten out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.22,0:13:29.18,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:32.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistaking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:36.28,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the mansion of the famous\Nantique art dealer, Mr. Richard Molly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:40.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it all mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:44.69,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,If caterpillar treads were the\Nway the gold bullion was carried off...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:45.63,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,strange, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:49.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember that Mr. Molly died\Nsuddenly in India ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:51.20,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:56.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that his son was with him\Nat the time and is still missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:13:58.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Then who lives in this mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:05.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, were you both customers\Nof my late husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:07.69,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it might be rude to just\Ndrop in on you like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.69,0:14:09.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,but we were in the neighbourhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.86,0:14:11.43,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.43,0:14:12.95,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It brings back memories\Nof my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.09,0:14:15.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's discuss and remember\Nmy husband after such a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.90,0:14:17.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:17.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:21.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I can certainly see he was an antique\Nart dealer who travelled the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:24.10,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,These are all very rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.24,0:14:25.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't trouble yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.77,0:14:27.00,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:33.41,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but do you\Nhave poor eyesight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.65,0:14:36.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but it's good to live a long life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:39.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:41.55,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd almost given up on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,0:14:42.68,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all of the sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:44.02,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Came back?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:45.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.09,0:14:49.26,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,My only son, who was missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.46,0:14:50.43,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.56,0:14:52.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He's really grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:55.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He even said he would\Nstay here forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.84,0:14:58.43,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds great.\NIs he here now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.61,0:15:02.60,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he is trying to finish his\Nrespected father's statue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:05.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He is hard at work in the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.18,0:15:07.41,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Statue?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.68,0:15:10.84,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's a statue made of fine gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:12.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What? A gold statue?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.99,0:15:18.02,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring him here.\NWhy don't you talk to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.13,0:15:19.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you don't have to rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.99,0:15:22.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We will visit the shop later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:25.56,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to talk more\Nabout your husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:26.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.64,0:15:31.30,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but I'd like\Nto call my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:32.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.18,0:15:37.54,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:43.31,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm running around everyday,\Neven checking out rat nests!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:45.42,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it turned out to be\Njust a waste of effort!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:46.95,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did they go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.12,0:15:48.02,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:48.92,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:50.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This had better be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.69,0:15:53.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a message from Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:56.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The message said it's good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:57.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! A message from Holmes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.03,0:15:58.60,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:15:59.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:00.43,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you say\Nso in the first place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:01.69,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:02.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You were what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:08.40,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the building over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:09.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:11.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps you could wait here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.85,0:16:13.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:16.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Please just wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.65,0:16:20.14,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.\NWhy can't I go into my son's shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.49,0:16:22.28,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's all right with you,\NI'll explain later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:25.68,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:28.02,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks a little complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:37.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't stop working!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:39.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The gold is going to harden!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:41.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.08,0:16:45.20,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,If you love your son,\Nfinish it as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:49.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The genius thief Moriarty's\Nonce-in-a-lifetime achievement.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:52.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,A golden statue to show my glory\Nto all of my descendants.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:56.81,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, don't listen to those guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.19,0:16:58.75,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Scream! Say whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:02.40,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The genius sculptor will\Nmake my golden statue!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:08.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do anything\Nunless we get Copit out first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.47,0:17:10.44,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I take care of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:12.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm excited, I haven't\Ndone this for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.64,0:17:13.73,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you take the roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:14.43,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.32,0:17:23.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:42.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:45.00,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys! Don't cut corners!\NWork harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.34,0:17:46.10,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:53.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Copit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:54.81,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Copit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.92,0:18:01.89,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you. Just be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:02.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.26,0:18:09.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you have to hide\Nsomewhere quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:12.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be mean to my Papa!\NI won't allow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:14.63,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:17.73,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! They found us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.84,0:18:20.10,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Todd, Smiley! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.27,0:18:20.64,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.77,0:18:21.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:25.21,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Moriarty, just give it up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.05,0:18:27.78,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You finally showed up, Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.88,0:18:29.31,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat him up first!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.18,0:18:30.81,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:31.54,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Drat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.62,0:18:33.31,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He always uses us so harshly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:35.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that will\Nhelp you get away?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:37.42,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on then!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:39.62,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you've got some guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:40.75,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.13,0:18:43.12,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he is strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.63,0:18:44.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:48.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.64,0:18:53.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,At least, I can carry the gold bullion\Nout while they're fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.74,0:18:57.04,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:07.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Drat! My precious gold bullion!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:19.09,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat! Did you do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.27,0:19:20.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to pick up the gold first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.54,0:19:23.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, aren't I strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:25.56,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Copit, you are great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:27.44,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.88,0:19:29.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:33.30,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.45,0:19:34.54,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Perison!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:35.41,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:38.15,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:43.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.52,0:19:44.25,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,And this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.24,0:20:04.30,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.73,0:20:28.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.84,0:20:30.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Open... sesame!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.51,0:20:34.91,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,- Wait!\N- Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.01,0:20:35.80,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.95,0:20:38.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Copit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:40.87,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Copit, watch out! Get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.35,0:20:45.88,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Copit, get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.45,0:20:47.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He is just an annoying brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:49.21,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, your papa's calling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.03,0:20:53.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! After them!\NAfter them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:57.62,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn about!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.38,0:21:11.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! That's the gold bullion!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:12.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Grab it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.71,0:21:13.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.38,0:21:20.08,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They're riding on my gold statue.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.63,0:21:31.46,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Let it go! Don't touch my gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.57,0:21:33.40,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'd let it go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.50,0:21:36.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You bums!\NDon't touch my gold statue!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.50,0:21:38.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Dolts! Take your hands off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:40.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:45.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Down! Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.35,0:21:46.64,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,All of it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.88,0:21:49.08,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Drat!\NAll that's left is my gold statue.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.29,0:22:00.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.93,0:22:04.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.64,0:22:17.34,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you Lestrade!\NYou took my gold statue!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:19.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want it, come down here!
