Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.16,0:23:45.13,Captions,,0000,0000,0000,,Executive Producer\NHENRY GOTO
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.20,0:23:47.17,Captions,,0000,0000,0000,,Producers\NSATOSHI FUJII, REIKO MATSUO\N& JONATHAN KLEIN
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.44,0:23:57.64,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,A two tailed snake...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.74,0:23:58.80,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,three lumps, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.91,0:24:00.07,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,two shiny eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.21,0:24:02.51,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,The seven hieroglyphs.\NWhat do they represent?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.72,0:24:06.05,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes pursues the mystery of\Nthe Wizard Sword of Saint Cross...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.12,0:24:09.21,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,in a dead heat\Nwith Professor Moriarty.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.89,0:24:12.26,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,But where is the treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.30,0:24:17.88,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,If you find yourself in a mystery,\Nplease come see us at Baker Street.
